{"tid":412514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"粗口辱罵長毛近3分鐘   陳淨心：影你老X","createTime":"2017-09-24T17:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T04:06:33.000Z","uid":48093,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36caace4626ef70b5694647b60897dc40942df72","tid":412514,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170925/large/1506269132_4027.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170925%2Flarge%2F1506269132_4027.png&h=38b99dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社民連前立法會議員「長毛」梁國雄，昨晚（24日）在佐敦巧遇愛港力成員陳淨心，被陳及其夥伴辱罵「Dog，這個走狗，漢奸」、「仲係度皮笑肉不笑，影乜X嘢」、「長毛賊」、「影影影，影你老味」等，不斷對梁人身攻擊。梁國雄全程冷靜地拍下過程，未有任何回應，從影片可見，梁被陳淨心等人辱罵至少2分半鐘，之後陳等人自行離開。<br />\n<br />\n梁至少被陳淨心和她的同伴共3至4人輪流辱罵，其間梁未有答嘴。陳淨心辱罵長毛近3分鐘，其間最少3次說，「影咩影，我唔驚你影」，並說：「影我個樣畀美國佬睇，暗殺我，笨」，但長毛始終沒有回應，陳最後沒趣自行離開。"},{"pid":"0bb6b5d45377db360dd5dc0952eb1637930e0239","tid":412514,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:35:46.000Z","msg":"其實佢呢種係邊一類精神病黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bb3e991ad23600cd3a57da96f68826548b5f33","tid":412514,"uid":100347,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T17:38:39.000Z","msg":"出動重案組查陳淨心講粗口未"},{"pid":"6da1f606e327aedfcf731745baed3703f08a0432","tid":412514,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:01:53.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"1297d655da731445f22da1ef8d8334eec2071894","tid":412514,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:05:11.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"80d32d07ed772205b24552f1368d4c0218765299","tid":412514,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:20:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 「影我個樣畀美國佬睇，暗殺我，笨」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.uncyc.org/zh-tw/thumb/9/9a/憎憲屎名言.jpg/300px-憎憲屎名言.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.uncyc.org%2Fzh-tw%2Fthumb%2F9%2F9a%2F%E6%86%8E%E6%86%B2%E5%B1%8E%E5%90%8D%E8%A8%80.jpg%2F300px-%E6%86%8E%E6%86%B2%E5%B1%8E%E5%90%8D%E8%A8%80.jpg&h=901bda9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你依挺傻屄打靶都晒子彈喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715d5414b210335802de45cc8b21a0303a557879","tid":412514,"uid":7534,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T22:18:49.000Z","msg":"Dog？做乜講英文？說好的愛国愛港呢？"},{"pid":"f6d4fa2d859e38f394bd1ebff2bfd96556cee8e4","tid":412514,"uid":39488,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T22:47:00.000Z","msg":"又粗口，又暴力，嚴重超越人類道德底線，快點叫我地嘅慈母仁愛高官出黎譴責呢條女人啦！"},{"pid":"4045a4d60e9f7f9594c87693c5e74f5454f00688","tid":412514,"uid":64948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T22:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢呢種係邊一類精神病黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n被害妄想症"},{"pid":"1e93340e39bffd72963604a8529ba132fecdd239","tid":412514,"uid":90704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T23:01:30.000Z","msg":"24小時開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做愛國人仕真是好敬業"},{"pid":"e7995688b0bfedeaf1e1c207ed34b68d06dd5e0c","tid":412514,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"唔知鬧一分鐘幾錢人工呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2828935892a0ff879e868a769e50ebafec77defc","tid":412514,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"呢排天氣熱啲蟲就走晒上嚟，真係麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aad59f4c858da4fb612e6a5ba787ade65cb0090","tid":412514,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"講粗口，即係支持港獨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"